<br>
Valquiss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubloodandsin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>bloodandsin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/3/02 2:36:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=975.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ethic question</span><hr size=1> For sake of argument I'll assume everyone is evil and a follower of hate and sin.  If anyone is good in the party, they are not worthy of rolling for any item in the world of Norrath, yet alone living.<br>
